meta {
  name: Current user (EDA)
  type: http
  seq: 14
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/eda/v1/users/me/
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{token}}
}

docs {
  EDA **`users/me`** profile for the bearer identity. On **AAP 2.6**, treat
  **system → Current user — gateway (me)** as the canonical platform identity;
  this endpoint reflects EDA’s view of the same principal.
}
